<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>[Admin] New User Pending Approval</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #333;
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 20px;
    }
    .header {
      background-color: #7c3aed;
      color: white;
      padding: 20px;
      text-align: center;
      border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0;
    }
    .content {
      background-color: #f9fafb;
      padding: 30px;
      border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
    }
    .highlight {
      background-color: #ede9fe;
      padding: 15px;
      border-radius: 6px;
      margin: 20px 0;
      border-left: 4px solid #7c3aed;
    }
    .user-details {
      background-color: white;
      padding: 15px;
      border-radius: 6px;
      margin: 20px 0;
      border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
    }
    .button {
      display: inline-block;
      background-color: #7c3aed;
      color: white;
      padding: 12px 24px;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 6px;
      margin-top: 20px;
      font-weight: bold;
    }
    .footer {
      text-align: center;
      margin-top: 30px;
      padding-top: 20px;
      border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #6b7280;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="header">
    <h1>[ADMIN] New User Pending Approval</h1>
  </div>

  <div class="content">
    <p>Hello Administrator,</p>

    <p>A new user has registered and is waiting for approval.</p>

    <div class="highlight">
      <p><strong>⚠️ Action Required:</strong> Please review the user details and approve or reject the registration.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="user-details">
      <p><strong>User Details:</strong></p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Name:</strong> {{firstName}} {{lastName}}</li>
        <li><strong>Email:</strong> {{email}}</li>
        <li><strong>Registration Date:</strong> {{registrationDate}}</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <p>Go to the admin panel to review and approve.</p>

    <a href="{{adminUrl}}" class="button">Open Admin Panel</a>

    <p style="margin-top: 30px;">
      <strong>Admin Panel - Boilerplate</strong>
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="footer">
    <p>This email was sent automatically by the system.</p>
    <p>&copy; 2025 Boilerplate. All rights reserved.</p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
